snippet.title: Minecraft x World Warrior: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Master the Hadouken in Minecraft with this Capcom-approved skin pack! 57Digital have created 35 iconic World Warrior skins, so you can conquer the Dark Had as Ryu, Ken, Chun-Li and more! With Character Creator items that include Ryu’s headband and Vega’s claws, as well as a free V shirt! The World Warrior skin pack is available in Minecraft Marketplace now! 

Requires the latest version of Minecraft: Bedrock Edition and access to Minecraft Marketplace (sold separately). Free item available for 60 days beginning 2/18/22; limit 1 per person/account.
